1_28	0.089361411	Plastic surgery is often recommended for patients who are 45 or older.
1_29	0.10285065	Plastic surgery uses incisions to cut the loose skin and fat off the face.
1_30	0.10146613	``It's not just stretching and pulling the skin,'' said Minas Constantinides, who is a plastic surgeon who works on face-lifts and is a member of the American Medical Association.
1_31	0.092761846	Face-lift surgery is an operation that costs between $7,000 and $20,000 and it lasts for years.
1_32	0.088863871	Acupuncture treatments would take at least 10 weeks to show improvement and do not assure a permanent physical change.
1_33	0.094307838	But with acupuncture the treatment is much cheaper, costing about $115 per session, at one session a week.
